                'references' => "Banerjee, A., Duflo, E., Glennerster, R., & Kinnan, C. (2015). The miracle of microfinance? Evidence from a randomized evaluation. American Economic Journal: Applied Economics, 7(1), 22–53.\nBateman, M. (2010). Why doesn't microfinance work? The destructive rise of local neoliberalism. Zed Books.\nGonzalez-Vega, C. (2011). Microfinance: Broadening access to financial services. Ohio State University AED Economics.\nYunus, M. (2007). Creating a world without poverty: Social business and the future of capitalism. PublicAffairs.",
