                'recommendations' => 'MFIs should integrate financial literacy modules into loan onboarding. Regulatory bodies should mandate flexible repayment options for ultra-poor borrowers. Future research should track children\'s educational outcomes as an indirect measure of household economic improvement.',
                'keywords' => 'microfinance, rural women, economic empowerment, Quezon Province, poverty alleviation, household income',
