                'title' => 'E-Commerce Adoption Barriers and Enablers Among Micro and Small Enterprises in Batangas',
                'college' => 'CBEA',
                'abstract' => 'This study identifies the key barriers and enablers of e-commerce adoption among micro and small enterprises (MSEs) in Batangas City, using the Technology Acceptance Model (TAM) as a theoretical lens to analyze owner attitudes, perceived usefulness, and adoption intentions.',
