                'conclusion' => 'Trust and digital skill gaps are the primary barriers to e-commerce adoption among MSEs in Batangas. TAM constructs of perceived ease of use and usefulness significantly predict adoption intention.',
                'recommendations' => 'DTI should expand digital literacy programs specifically targeting MSE owners. E-marketplace platforms should simplify onboarding processes and provide local-language support. Future research should track actual adoption behavior beyond intention.',
